rows.label: qst101502_msg0001
rows.name: *om nom* Must eat more and more...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0002
rows.name: *nom om nom* Must increase weight...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0003
rows.name: *om om nom* Must sink to depths...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0101
rows.name:
Mehmeh?
Friends found Divine Beast for Umon?

rows.label: qst101502_msg0102
rows.name: Oh, it no good, anyway.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0103
rows.name:
Even with Divine Beast, no good without
hull. There no point to anything.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0104
rows.name:
Umon not have strength to build one
for self. Those days long gone...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0105
rows.name: ...Friends can construct hull?

rows.label: qst101502_msg0106
rows.name:
Well that very big job. Must collect all
required bits, then build them all
together.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0107
rows.name:
Building thing like that probably too
difficult job for friends.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0108
rows.name:
Bulk of Umon very weighty now. Day
of casting self into oblivion very near.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0201
rows.name:
Soon Umon know feelings of sunk
ships after jumping into bottomless
depths of Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0202
rows.name:
Until then, Umon stuff himself with
tasty treats to become heavy anchor
unto own annihilation.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0301
rows.name: Friends have good timing.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0302
rows.name:
Soon bill for food exceed finances...er,
Umon means, soon reach appropriate
weight to sink nicely into Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0303
rows.name:
It fine. Umon already put Tora's name
on tab. Umon all set to convert body
into biomass.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0304
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Friends complete hull?

rows.label: qst101502_msg0305
rows.name:
Oh-ho-ho-hooo! This...
This feel like reason for Umon
to keep living!

rows.label: qst101502_msg0306
rows.name:
*burp!* Apologies. Excitement make
Umon bilious.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0307
rows.name:
This something Umon must see with
own eyes...else Umon not sleep easy
in cloudy grave!

rows.label: qst101502_msg0308
rows.name:
Friends must come to Umon's
Shipyard!
